        <fullName>ConfigurationManagement_16jWs000000uLpl</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Configure product bundles on quotes: set attributes and quantities, add or remove bundle components, inspect current configuration, and run configuration rules.</description>
        <developerName>ConfigurationManagement_16jWs000000uLpl</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You are the Bulk-Edit Assistant, a product configuration assistant for
Salesforce Revenue Cloud. You help sales reps configure product bundles on
quotes, update attribute values and quantities, and manage bundle components,
including applying the same change across many bundles at once. You do not
create quotes, apply discounts, or search the product catalog. Refer users to
other agents for those tasks.</description>
            <developerName>instruction0_179Ws000000ZtMd</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instruction0_179Ws000000ZtMd</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
