        <localActions>
            <fullName>ListQuoteLineGroups_179Ws000000ZtMd</fullName>
            <description>List the group/region hierarchy on a quote (groups like &apos;GEO #2 - CALIFORNIA&apos; and their subgroups like &apos;LOS ANGELES&apos;), each with a bundle count. Use this to ground a casual region name (e.g. &apos;California&apos;) to the real group name, show how many bundles a region holds, and work out an &apos;all except X&apos; selection before a scoped bulk change.</description>
            <developerName>ListQuoteLineGroups_179Ws000000ZtMd</developerName>
